How this file is used

During analysis (Step 1): The Content Strategist reads this calendar and flags if a proposed topic overlaps with something published in the last 30 days.
After approval (Step 4): Each approved piece is added here with its publish date, channel, title, one-line summary, and thematic pillar(s).
Cleanup: At the start of each session, entries older than 30 days from today's date are removed.
